high_descs: Turn right, walk to the door, then turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open the fridge, take out the dark mug from the third shelf, then close the door.
Turn around completely and walk up to the table.
Place the mug down on the table, to the left of the beer mug.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is sitting in front of the potato on the table.
Place the knife in the dark mug that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife inside of a chilled mug on the table.

high_descs: Move to the right to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the black mug inside, and close the refrigerator.
Turn around and go straight to face the white kitchen table.
Place the mug on top of the table.
Pick the knife up from off of the table.
Place the knife inside of the black mug.
anns.task_desc: Place the knife inside of the chilled black mug.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the door, turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the black cup on the bottom shelf, and close the refrigerator door.
Turn completely around and walk to the table.
Put the cup on the table just left of the orange glass on the front edge.
Pick up the large knife behind the orange glass.
Put the knife in the cup with the blade down.
anns.task_desc: Get the cup from the refrigerator and put the big knife in it.
